snippet.title: Top Gun: The Second Mission NES Commercial # 2
snippet.description: Top Gun: The Second Mission, released in Japan as Top Gun: Dual Fighters, is the second Top Gun game produced by Konami for the NES. It was released in Japan on December 15, 1989, in North America on January 1990, and in Europe and Australia on October 24, 1991.
